// Helper for `static-bare-stmt-cross-module`. Exports a static that
// the importing module's `static recordSetup()` reads indirectly
// through a function call. If PR 2.5's depth-1 expansion missed the
// dep edge, `recordSetup` would see `initialized` as uninitialized
// and PR 1's read-before-init trap would fire instead of "yes".
export static const initialized = "yes"
